      <MissionDescription>The HOPE Center's mission is to "Fight hunger and Feed HOPE" to families living in poverty by providing (1) groceries to families in need, (2) job training and job placement for unemployed, and (3) hope in the hearts of children with our fine arts after-school program.</MissionDescription>
